<function>

access:   public

name: locale

param: mixed, $value

param: bool, $blank, false

return: bool

</function>

Validate that a value is a locale code.

* Parameters:

 * mixed //$value//: The value to validate.

 * bool //$blank//: Allow blank values to be valid.

* Returns bool: True if valid, false if not.

Validate that a value is a locale code.

Note that this overrides Solar_Base::locale().

The format is two lower-case letters, an underscore, and two upper-case
letters.